data.description: Indulge in the captivating allure of this remarkable 5-bedroom, 3-bath home, perfectly nestled in an exceptional location alongside an elementary school and parks. As you step inside, be greeted by the delightful sight of new carpet and flooring, harmoniously accentuating the abundant natural light that permeates every corner. Upstairs, three inviting bedrooms await, while the large primary suite is ready for your personal touches. Cozy up in the basement living room by the pellet stove or unwind by the wood-burning fireplace in the family room. The tranquil hot tub beckons for relaxation, and the generously-sized yard provides ample space for outdoor activities. Savor the delightful and delicious apples plucked fresh from the tree. Don't miss this extraordinary opportunity to call this residence your own. Additionally, enjoy the convenience of nearby shopping, restaurants, parks, and schools. Please note that the two basement bedrooms are non-conforming. New AC installed 9/3/2023
